text: The Australian Labor Party (Australian Capital Territory Branch), commonly known as ACT Labor, is the Australian Capital Territory branch of the Australian Labor Party, a centre-left social democratic political party in Australia. It is currently in Government in a coalition with the Greens. The party's leader is Andrew Barr (who is the current Chief Minister) and the party's deputy leader is Yvette Berry.
